### Description

This is my current [`solidity_ls`](https://github.com/juanfranblanco/vscode-solidity) configuration:
```lua
    settings = {
      solidity = {
        compileUsingRemoteVersion = '0.8.26',
        defaultCompiler = 'remote',
        enabledAsYouTypeCompilationErrorCheck = true,
      },
    },
```
Version: `vscode-solidity-server@0.0.179`

Unfortunately, by looking at the logs, it looks like its being ignored and compiling using the latest solidity version, embedded compiler (just the defaults). There's also some ERROR there which doesn't provide many details but it seems related.

